# Parsing JSON Requests

Express does not automatically understand JSON data sent by a client.

To enable JSON parsing, the following middleware was added inside:

```text
backend/src/app.js
```

```javascript
app.use(express.json());
```

This middleware tells Express to automatically convert incoming JSON into a JavaScript object.

Without this middleware:

```javascript
req.body
```

would be:

```javascript
undefined
```

After adding the middleware, JSON sent from Postman became available inside:

```javascript
req.body
```

