# Current Product API

At the end of this session, the Products API supports:

| Method | Endpoint        | Purpose                              |
| ------ | --------------- | ------------------------------------ |
| GET    | `/products`     | Return all products stored in memory |
| GET    | `/products/:id` | Return one product by its index      |
| POST   | `/products`     | Add a new product to memory          |

The application now supports the **Create** and **Read** parts of CRUD.

The remaining operations (**Update** and **Delete**) will be implemented in the next session.

